        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "主，借你这名的无比，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "恩典不至渐疲倦；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "今日、昨天，你不更易，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你是一样到永远！"
            }
          ]
        }
